'''Guide: An Introductory Guide to Global Citizen Media'''

URL = http://www.globalvoicesonline.org/2008/01/16/an-introductory-guide-to-global-citizen-media/


=Description=

"Rising Voices announces the first in a series of outreach guides meant
to explain the fundamentals of citizen media to a non-technical
readership. The first guide, An Introduction to Citizen Media, offers
context and case studies which show how everyday citizens across the
world are increasingly using blogs, podcasts, online video, and
digital photography to engage in an unmediated conversation which
transcends borders, cultures, and differing languages."


